<A>__{the fog creeps through, casting an eerie twilight pall. an armed search party moves along the street. they glance down an alley on the far side is another search party. the men nod to each other, continue on. a moment, and then jack drops from his hiding place beneath the eaves of a building. he still wears the manacles. across the street is a shop with barn doors, a pass thru door set in the middle. above is a sign with a black anvil.}
